WEBVTT

00:04:34.520 --> 00:04:35.676
(Musik Berakhir)

00:04:35.676 --> 00:04:36.468
(Tepuk tangan)

00:04:36.468 --> 00:04:37.482
Terima kasih.

00:04:38.080 --> 00:04:41.056
(Tepuk tangan)

00:04:41.080 --> 00:04:42.200
Tapi masih banyak lagi,

00:04:43.040 --> 00:04:44.630
(Tawa)

00:04:45.680 --> 00:04:49.736
Dua fitur musik,
yaitu nada dan ritme,

00:04:49.760 --> 00:04:52.046
mereka adalah dua versi
dari hal yang sama.

00:04:52.280 --> 00:04:53.261
Saya tunjukkan.

00:04:53.520 --> 00:04:54.736
(Irama lambat)

00:04:54.760 --> 00:04:55.960
Itu ritme kan?

00:04:57.478 --> 00:04:59.046
Perhatikan ketika kita percepat.

00:04:59.360 --> 00:05:02.576
(Irama semakin cepat)